{
  "script_id": "coupon-collector",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "前几张总是很快到手，可越到后面，越难抽到没有的那几张。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "setup",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "setup-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/setup-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "假设一共有 n 种赠券，每次随机抽到其中一种，机会均等。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "setup",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "setup-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/setup-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "我们关心的是：平均要抽多少次，才能集齐全部 n 种？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "setup",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "setup-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/setup-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "图上的阶梯线，就是已集齐种数随抽取次数的增长过程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "expect",
      "line_id": "exp-1",
      "filename": "expect-exp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/expect-exp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.56,
      "size": 57024,
      "text": "收集第 k 种新券时，还差的种类占比是 (n−k+1)/n，平均要抽 n/(n−k+1) 次。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "expect",
      "line_id": "exp-2",
      "filename": "expect-exp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/expect-exp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "把每一步的期望加起来，总期望正好是 n 乘以调和数 H(n)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "expect",
      "line_id": "exp-3",
      "filename": "expect-exp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/expect-exp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "H(n) 是 1 加二分之一加三分之一，一直加到 n 分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "tail",
      "line_id": "tail-1",
      "filename": "tail-tail-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/tail-tail-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.74,
      "size": 43776,
      "text": "由于 H(n) 约等于 ln(n)，总期望大约是 n 乘以 ln(n)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "tail",
      "line_id": "tail-2",
      "filename": "tail-tail-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/tail-tail-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.78,
      "size": 44496,
      "text": "注意最后一张，平均要抽整整 n 次才能碰上，这正是曲线尾部越来越平的原因。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "调整赠券的种类数，看期望次数怎样随之攀升。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "反复点击再模拟，感受每一次集齐所需的次数在期望值附近波动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "集齐 n 种赠券的期望次数是 n 乘以调和数 H(n)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "它约等于 n 乘 ln(n)，收尾阶段总是格外漫长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "coupon-collector",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/coupon-collector/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "下次抽卡凑不齐时，你会知道那是数学的必然，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 33.010000000000005,
  "total_size": 528048
